### Test GraphQL endpoint is working
POST http://localhost:5001/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query { __type(name: \"Query\") { name } }"
}

### Test getting current repositories  
POST http://localhost:5001/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "query GetRepositories { repositories { id name url status language description createdAt updatedAt } }"
}

### Test adding a simple repository (GitHub Hello World)
POST http://localhost:5001/graphql
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "mutation AddRepository($input: AddRepositoryInput!) { addRepository(input: $input) { id name url language description status createdAt updatedAt } }",
  "variables": {
    "input": {
      "url": "https://github.com/octocat/Hello-World"
    }
  }
}

